The bathroom was on the small size with shower over the bath.	The bathroom was the highlight, fairly basic and clean but small with meagre towels and toiletries.	The shower however was very touchy and the water was either scalding hot or very cold.	The bathroom was small and not as contemporary as I was expecting.	The toilet did not flush properly and the shower seemed to have only 2 temperatures: scalding hot or freezing cold.	The room was clean and the bed was very comfortable.	Also had a problem with the shower - very hot...but not an issue.	The bed was comfortable with lots of pillows.	My only quibbles were with the bathroom.